metadata.name: Trippy Apepe YC #1
metadata.description: Trippy Apepe YC is a limited collection of 333 1/1 NFTs available on the Ethereum blockchain. TAYC Offers Staking, The Trippy Marketplace (8080 Dev Team), Community Votes (DAO), Competitive Games, and a great network of individuals to build within the web 3 community.
